### 1. Register a New User
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "studybuddy2",
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###

### 2. Login to Get Your JWT Access Token
# @name login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "studybuddy2",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

###

### 3. Test Protected To-Do Creation
# Paste your raw access token string right after 'Bearer'
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/todos/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzgwNDEyNTA5LCJpYXQiOjE3ODA0MDg5MDksImp0aSI6IjQ3ZDBiMmM4ZTY5ZTRlZTNiODI1NjcwNDBjMWYzOTQ4IiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjEwIn0.53fE9oc9UwDnwvgD2cmHn4WiuIcXQ_CZHBImSY6zdfA

{
  "task": "Test Todo via VS Code",
  "is_done": false
}

###

### 4. Fetch All Your To-Dos
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/todos/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ0b2tlbl90eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzgwNDEyNTA5LCJpYXQiOjE3ODA0MDg5MDksImp0aSI6IjQ3ZDBiMmM4ZTY5ZTRlZTNiODI1NjcwNDBjMWYzOTQ4IiwidXNlcl9pZCI6IjEwIn0.53fE9oc9UwDnwvgD2cmHn4WiuIcXQ_CZHBImSY6zdfA

